units lj
atom_style sphere
boundary p p p
lattice fcc 0.4
region box block 0 5 0 5 0 5
create_box 1 box
create_atoms 1 box
set group all diameter 1.0 density 1.0
pair_style brownian 1.0 1 1 2.5 2.5 1.0 12345
pair_coeff * *
neighbor 0.3 bin
fix 1 all nve/sphere
timestep 0.0001
thermo 5
thermo_style custom step temp epair etotal press
thermo_modify format float %20.15g
run 20
